Anglo Catholic is a member of the [[Church of England]], however, its ritual is more like [[Roman Catholic Church]]. They look like [[Roman Catholic]], except the part that they do not recognise the [[Bishop of Rome]], or [[Pope]]. It is one of the high-church in the [[Church of England]].

The founders include [[John Henry Newman]], who eventually joined the [[Roman Catholic Church]] himself, and become a [[cardinal]] in the [[Roman Catholic Church]].